If you are someone who works at an office daily you are someone who understands the importance of a pen. People end up losing a lot of pens in offices schools and colleges. Some forget them some lose them some get borrowed but never get returned. But what does one do? Well the answer is simple…you can buy the Universal Speedex use and throw ballpoint pens!

These pens are made from recyclable plastic and do not give you the option of changing the refill. With an outer shell made from plastic the Universal SpeedEx ball point pens are sturdy enough to withstand daily use and abuse. The ink is contained in an inner cavity inside the pen’s outer shell. The cavity has been designed to encourage uninterrupted flow of ink. This ensures a non-stop uninterrupted writing experience for anyone that uses it. Made by Universal the pens are designed to be use and throw. Sold at a very economical price the Universal Speedex use and throw pens will not break anyone’s pocket. Universal has been providing its market with stationary solutions for almost a few years now. With the same customer satisfaction and drive for innovation Universal brings to you the Speedex use and throw pens.

Features

  • Sturdy - Made from biodegradable plastic shells the pens do not get easily damaged and will endure most of the abuse thrown its way.
  • Use and Throw - The economical price and biodegradable construction ensures that the pens don’t break pockets and nor do they harm the environment when they are disposed of.
  • Available in Various Colours - The Universal Speedex use and throw pens come in various different colours ensuring that you can get the colour of your choice.

Technical Specifications
